about.summary: Python library for importing the Extensible Data Format (XDF)

name: pyxdf
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyxdf" %}
{% set version = "1.15.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c4a2fe9058274e3da7637b0f4afcf54365a616a6cd71333eb5e18e94caa7c86b

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - setuptools
    - setuptools_scm
  run:
    - python
    - numpy
    - setuptools

test:
  imports:
    - pyxdf
    - pyxdf.pyxdf

about:
  home: https://github.com/xdf-modules/xdf-Python
  license: BSD-2-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Python library for importing the Extensible Data Format (XDF)'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hoechenberger
